en: Source filters can be used to exclude one or more fields when fetching the document source. This happens when viewing a document in the Discover app, or with a table displaying results from a saved search in the Dashboard app. Each row is built using the source of a single document, and if you have documents with large or unimportant fields you may benefit from filtering those out at this lower level.
cn: 源筛选器可以在获取源文档时排除一个或多个字段。这种情况发生在查看应用程序中的文档时或者显示在仪表板应用程序中保存的查询结果时显示的结果时。每一行都是使用一个文档的源来构建的，如果您拥有具有较大或不重要字段的文档，则可以从较低级别筛选出这些文件。

en: Note that multi-fields will incorrectly appear as matches in the table below. These filters only actually apply to fields in the original source document, so matching multi-fields are not actually being filtered.
cn: 注意多个字段可能将出现如下表匹配。这些过滤器实际上只适用于原始源文档中的字段，因此匹配的多个字段实际上没有被过滤。

en: source filter, accepts wildcards (e.g., `user*` to filter fields starting with 'user')

en: From here you can delete saved objects, such as saved searches. You can also edit the raw data of saved objects. Typically objects are only modified via their associated application, which is probably what you should use instead of this screen. Each tab is limited to 100 results. You can use the filter to find objects not in the default list.
cn: 从这里您可以删除已保存的对象，例如已保存的历史查询。您也可以编辑已保存对象的原始数据。通常，对象只能通过相关的应用程序进行修改，这可能是您应该使用的，而不是在这个屏幕。每个表仅展示100个结果。你可以使用筛选器来查找不在默认列表中的对象。

en: Modifying objects is for advanced users only. Object properties are not validated and invalid objects could cause errors, data loss, or worse. Unless someone with intimate knowledge of the code told you to be in here, you probably shouldn’t be.
cn: 修改对象只适用于高级用户。未验证对象属性，无效对象可能导致错误、数据丢失或更糟。除非有一个熟悉此操作的人告诉你要在这里操作，您不应该独自修改对象。

en:
Be careful in here, these settings are for very advanced users only.
          Tweaks you make here can break large portions of Kibana. Some of these
          settings may be undocumented, unsupported or experimental. If a field has a default value,
          blanking the field will reset it to its default which
          may be unacceptable given other configuration directives. Deleting a
          custom setting will permanently remove it from Kibana's config.

en: 'APM (Application Performance Monitoring) automatically collects in-depth' + ' performance metrics and errors from inside your applications.'
cn: 'APM (应用程序性能监控) 自动从应用程序中收集深入的性能指标和错误。'

en: ${apmIntro} APM consists of three components - the Agents, the Server, and the UI:\n
cn: ${apmIntro} APM包含3个组件 - 代理、服务器和用户界面：\n

en: '* The Agents are libraries in your application that run inside of your application process.\n'
cn: '* 代理是运行在您的应用程序进程内部的应用程序库。\n'

en: '* The Server processes data from agents and stores the application data in Elasticsearch.\n'
cn: '* 服务器处理来自于代理的数据并且存储应用程序数据到Elasticsearch。\n'

en: '* The UI is the dedicated APM UI (X-Pack Basic) and preconfigured dashboards.\n\n'
cn: '* 用户界面是专用的APM UI（基于X-pack）和预先配置的仪表盘。\n\n'

cn: 'Apache2 Filebeat模块解析Apache 2 HTTP服务器创建的访问日志和错误日志。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-apache2.html)' + ' 关于Apache2模块。'

cn: '`MySQL` Filebeat解析由MySQL创建的错误和变慢日志。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-mysql.html)' + ' 关于`MySQL`模块。'

en: shortDescription: 'Collect and parse access and error logs created by the Nginx HTTP server.'
cn: shortDescription: '收集和解析由Nginx HTTP服务器创建的访问日志和错误日志。'

en: 'The `nginx` Filebeat module parses access and error logs created by the Nginx HTTP server.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-nginx.html)' + ' about the nginx module.'
cn: '`Nginx` Filebeat模块解析由Nginx HTTP服务器创建的访问日志和错误日志。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-nginx.html)' + ' 关于Nginx模块。'

en: shortDescription: 'Collect and parse error and slow logs created by Redis.'
cn: shortDescription: '收集和解析由Redis创建的错误和变慢日志。'

en: 'The `redis` Filebeat module parses error and slow logs created by Redis.' + ' For Redis to write error logs, make sure the `logfile` option, from the' + ' Redis configuration file, is set to `redis-server.log`.' + ' The slow logs are read directly from Redis via the `SLOWLOG` command.' + ' For Redis to record slow logs, make sure the `slowlog-log-slower-than`' + ' option is set.' + ' Note that the `slowlog` fileset is experimental.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-redis.html)' + ' about the `redis` module.'
cn: '`Redis` Filebeat模块解析由Redis创建的错误日志和变慢日志。' + ' 要让Redis记录错误日志，请确保Redis配置文件中的`logfile`选项被设置为`redis-server.log`。' + ' 变慢日志可以通过`SLOWLOG`命令从Redis直接读取。' + ' 要让Redis记录变慢日志，请确保`slowlog-log-slower-than`' + ' 选项已被设置。' + ' 请注意`slowlog`是实验选项。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-redis.html)' + ' 关于`Redis`模块。'

en: shortDescription: 'Collect and parse logs written by the local Syslog server.'
cn: shortDescription: '收集和分析由服务器日志服务记录的日志。'

en: 'The `system` Filebeat module collects and parses logs created by the system logging service of common ' + ' Unix/Linux based distributions. This module is not available on Windows.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-system.html)' + ' about the `system` module.'
cn: '`System` Filebeat收集和解析由常见的基于Unix/Linux的系统日志服务记录的日志。 此模块并不适用于Windows。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.filebeat}/filebeat-module-system.html)' + ' 关于`System`模块。'

en: shortDescription: 'Collects CPU, memory, network, and disk statistics from the host.',
cn: shortDescription: '从目标主机上收集的CPU、内存、网络、磁盘统计信息。',

en: 'The `system` Metricbeat module collects CPU, memory, network, and disk statistics from the host.' + ' It collects system wide statistics as well as per process and per filesystem statistics.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-system.html)' + ' about the system module.'
cn: '`System` Metricbeat模块从目标主机上收集的CPU、内存、网络、磁盘统计信息。' + ' 它收集系统范围的统计信息，以及每个进程和每个文件系统的统计数据。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-system.html)' + ' 关于system模块。'

en: 'The `redis` Metricbeat module fetches internal metrics from the Redis server.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-redis.html)' + ' about the redis module.'
cn: '`Redis` Metricbeat模块从Redis服务器内部获取指标。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-redis.html)' + ' 关于redis模块。'

cn: shortDescription: '从Nginx HTTP服务器内部获取指标。',

en: 'The `nginx` Metricbeat module fetches internal metrics from the Nginx HTTP server.' + ' The module scrapes the server status data from the web page generated by the' + ' [ngx_http_stub_status_module](http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_stub_status_module.html)' + ' module, which needs to be enabled in you Nginx installation.' + ' [Learn more]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-nginx.html)' + ' about the nginx module.'
cn: '`Nginx` Metricbeat模块从Nginx HTTP服务器内部获取指标。' + ' 此模块从通过' + ' [ngx_http_stub_status_module](http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_stub_status_module.html)' + ' 模块生成的网页上获取服务器状态数据，此模块需要您在Nginx安装时启用。' + ' [学习更多]({config.docs.beats.metricbeat}/metricbeat-module-nginx.html)' + ' 关于Nginx模块。'

en: shortDescription: 'Collect Netflow records sent by a Netflow exporter',

'The Logstash Netflow module simplifies the collection, normalization, and visualization of network flow data. ' + 'With a single command, the module parses network flow data, indexes the events into Elasticsearch, and installs a suite of Kibana ' + 'dashboards to get you exploring your data immediately. Logstash modules support Netflow Version 5 and 9. [Learn more]' + '({config.docs.logstash}/netflow-module.html) about the Netflow module'
cn: 'LogStash NetFlow模块简化了收集、规范化，以及网络流量数据的可视化。 ' + '使用一条简单的命令，此模块将会解析网络流量数据，索引事件到Elasticsearch并安装一个Kibana仪表盘套件' + '让您可以立即分析您的数据。Logstash模块支持Netflow版本5和9。 [学习更多]' + '({config.docs.logstash}/netflow-module.html) 关于Netflow模块。'
